  "texts": [
    "With existing facilities, such observations are expensive and impractical for long monitoring periods, therefore, predictions and early detection of the onset of HMEs and their peaks are mandatory to trigger multi-wavelength follow-up.",
    "An alert system has been used by OGLE (Woźniak et al. 2000) and a triggering mechanism for multi-band follow-up has been proposed by Wyithe et al. (2000b).",
    "However, such prediction algorithms have not been used extensively and as of yet there has not been any clear prediction and detailed follow-up of a HME as it unfolds, i.e.",
    "predicting the peak from light curves like those shown in Fig. 24 and scheduling detailed observations accordingly (spectroscopy, X-ray spectra and imaging, etc).",
    "This could also be attributed to using only just a single band as the base signal from which to predict HMEs."
  ],
  "correct_citations": [
    "An alert system has been used by OGLE (Woźniak et al. 2000) and a triggering mechanism for multi-band follow-up has been proposed by Wyithe et al. (2000b)."
  ]
